Nigerian skit maker, Debo Adedayo, has announced his engagement ceremony and wedding date. The comedian disclosed this on Saturday via his Instagram page, by unveiling several pictures of himself and his partner in traditional outfit. He wrote, “Engagement today, wedding tomorrow.” However, his fans are uncertain about his statement in regards to the supposed engagement and wedding, as they believed it to be pictures from a skit video. Several celebrities such as Kate Henshaw, Ada Ameh, Mary Lazarus, Small Doctor, Yul Edochie, Nkechi Blessing and many more were seen congratulating the comedian in the comment section. POLL